Package: scimagR
Title: Spinal Cord Injury Imaging Pipeline for MRI and CT Analysis in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("R.", "Heller", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                   email = "raban.heller@example.com")
Description: An end-to-end pipeline for longitudinal MRI and CT analysis
    in spinal cord injury (SCI) research. Provides R wrappers for the
    Spinal Cord Toolbox (SCT) including SCIsegV2 lesion segmentation,
    DICOM anonymization and NIfTI conversion tools, SCI-specific clinical
    metrics (MSCC, compression ratio, tissue bridge quantification),
    implant artifact grading, and pipeline orchestration with built-in
    quality control. Integrates with workflowr for reproducible,
    publication-ready neuroimaging analyses.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/cttir/scimagR
BugReports: https://github.com/cttir/scimagR/issues
